    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle that serves as a dependable and comfortable drive. The car is in good overall condition, showing that it has been cared for over the years. You'll find some minor signs of use, such as light stone chips on the front bumper and some slight creasing on the leather seating surfaces, but nothing that detracts from its overall appeal. Mechanically, it is sound, with a smooth engine and transmission, and all electronics are fully functional. This is a solid choice for someone looking for a high-quality vehicle that is ready for the road without needing immediate attention.",
