    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a legacy of iron and elegance. This isn't merely a vehicle; it\u2019s a symphony of mechanical poetry, waiting for its next conductor. The engine breathes with a rhythmic, soulful pulse that speaks of long, winding roads and the golden hour of sunset. Its silhouette cuts through the mundane, a timeless testament to a more sophisticated era. Inside, the cabin welcomes you with the comforting scent of aged leather and the quiet dignity of a machine that has seen the world but is far from finished. It carries the graceful patina of a life well-lived, offering a raw, visceral driving experience that modern cars have long since forgotten. This is your invitation to own a piece of automotive history that doesn't just drive\u2014it inspires.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience the perfect blend of performance and sophistication with this meticulously maintained vehicle. Representing exceptional value, this car has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for safety and road-readiness. Its sleek exterior and well-appointed interior reflect a history of careful ownership, making it an ideal choice for the discerning driver who demands quality without compromise. Sophisticated, reliable, and impressively presented, this vehicle stands as a testament to enduring automotive excellence.",
      "price": 34900.0,
