    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey neighbor! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. She\u2019s been my trusty companion on many weekend cruises and has never let me down. While she\u2019s got a few tiny signs of being well-loved over the years\u2014just a bit of character, really\u2014she still turns heads and drives like a dream. I\u2019ve kept her serviced and clean because a car this fun deserves the best. If you're looking for a reliable, soulful ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, come take a look. I'd love to see her go to someone who will enjoy her as much as I have!",
      "price": 36500.0,
